parameters.name: query
parameters.value:
SELECT patient.public_id
    FROM pkbperson AS professional
    INNER JOIN personcontact AS pc ON professional.id = pc.person_id
    INNER JOIN instituteuser AS iu ON professional.id = iu.person_id
    INNER JOIN patientconsent AS consent ON iu.institute_id = consent.accessingteamorpersonid
    INNER JOIN pkbperson AS patient ON consent.patientpersonid = patient.id
    INNER JOIN nationalid AS nid ON patient.id = nid.person_id
    WHERE
        pc.contactvalue = 'az.pro.1@pkbtest.com' AND consent.accessingentitytype = 'TEAM'
        AND nid.type = 'NHS_NUMBER' AND nid.value = '5193233945'
